message.body: Eden. Dana says they give a prize per week for text message! She doesn't think anyone gave this week. We have to do it.
Ok. Is it something I can do on my own? Or will I mess it up? Haha.
I'll do it with you. We can't forget
How long does it take?
I don't know

So can you do me a favor? Either when you go out to get lunch or after work, could you stop and get a pack of sponges? I'm using our last one and it's pretty worn out. But anywhos, you warned me about dried up rat pee. The bowls with the pink flowers that I like we're splattered with what I at first thought looked like egg yolk. Came off too easy. So it dawned on me that it might be rat pee! I don't know if you were joking with me or telling the truth, but can you get us new sponges please?
So that's everything I've done. I got the box of unopened tall glasses to do. Then I think I'm done for today.
I want koriana
And what's really getting me to crave it is that little bowl of tepid garlic soup. Hats.
Hahaha I love you
Do you really want Koreana?
Yeah. So I'm trying to figure out what I want to do. Because I am spent from those dishes and feel like I'm going to fall asleep.
You better not!
I just need to lay down for a bit before getting ready.
I'm going to leave in about an hour. Is that okay?
Yeah
Wait what time?
Like 4:45?
Or do you want me to be there at five?
Because I'm pretty much ready. I just need to get changed.
Its up to you. Getting here earlier will give us more time
Ok
And I wanted to go tio the show early for good seat
I'll let you know when I'm on my way
Okay
Waiting for the train.
Okay
Downstairs
Do you mind coming up?
I just want to finish something
Ok you have to get me?
I'm with Michael.
